Experms changelog

Version 0.5
 - 2013-08-21 - Fixed a bug that prevented taking the actual owner and group id not definded in the config

Version 0.4
 - 2013-08-21 - Fixed a bug that prevented 'restore' and 'dircount' from working

Version 0.3
 - 2013-08-21 - Rewrote the whole thing in Python. Nothing is the same as before ;-)
     Advantages:
      - doesn't crash ;-)
      - much faster
      - more lightweight
      - handle nested directories
      - exclude files and folders
      - exclude files based on a pattern (regex)
      - more intuitive configuration

Version 0.2
 - 2013-01-26 - Fixed the annoying bug that prevented Experms from being started again after a reboot or crash
